[I] A maintained version of DDRace

[T] DDraceNetwork (DDNet) is an actively maintained version of DDRace, a
[T] Teeworlds modification with a unique cooperative gameplay. Help each
[T] other play through custom maps with up to 64 players, compete against the
[T] best in international tournaments, design your own maps, or run your own
[T] server. The official servers are around the world. All ranks made on
[T] official servers are available worldwide and you can collect points!

[U] https://ddnet.org

[A] ddnet.org
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/game

[E] opt libopus

[L] ZLIB
[V] 19.8.2

[D] 0589807ad5ceeba5abbf1f048b22fef41e8d16787c1926b579a9bdb7 ddnet-19.8.2.tar.gz https://github.com/ddnet/ddnet/archive/refs/tags/19.8.2/

